data.description: This is a unique and amazing opportunity to own a well maintained home that was originally built in 1930. With a beautiful wrap around front porch to enjoy your corner lot with beautiful oak trees surrounding over an acre! Home features tile throughout the downstairs, restored natural wood floors up the stairs and hallways. A carpet runner on the stairs and in bedrooms. With charming features throughout the home you'll want to book it to see its beauty in person! An outdoor shop with water and electric hookup. Also, a large 2 garage door metal building for whatever you might need. With great local restaurants nearby and a boat dock just a few miles away get ready to fall in love and make your own story here!
